district court in washington on monday charged that burger king 
also gave white operators more favorable financing terms 
blacks were charged as much as twice what white operators paid 
to purchase or lease stores and equipment the lawsuit said 
joyce myers a burger king spokeswoman said monday we cant 
really respond until we have had an opportunity to see the suit and 
evaluate what the allegations are 
