according to cooper twothirds of the work was taken directly 
from beethovens sketches which sometimes were nothing more than a 
single line of notes 
theres something of beethoven in every bar he said you 
cant say beethoven stops here and cooper starts there in 
practically every bar its part beethoven and part me 
