stopped advancing toward the wildlife waystation a shelter for 
1000 exotic animals that have been abandoned or wandered into 
neighborhoods 
its still a longrange threat cautioned robert brady a 
spokesman for the us forest service 
it looks like we have survived this one well weve made it 
said martine colett owner of the shelter my face is a picture 
of wonderfulness 
the lions tigers giraffes jaguars horses alligators and 
